00:54:18,451 --> 00:54:21,840
*brachah* of חכמה *chochmah*, we mention God gives us intellect, and then

1118
00:54:21,840 --> 00:54:24,660
we say מבדיל בין קודש לחול *mavdil bein kodesh l'chol*, and then

1119
00:54:24,660 --> 00:54:25,460
we end

1120
00:54:27,160 --> 00:54:30,240
with we end with the ברכה *brachah*. Why? Because the end of

1121
00:54:30,240 --> 00:54:32,480
the ברכה *brachah* we're already making a בקשה bakasha *bakashah*. By the

